    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "伊金霍洛旗文物局：",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": null,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "根据《中华人民共和国文物保护法》及《内蒙古自治区文物保护条例》有关规定，内蒙古西部天然气股份有限公司委托第三方勘探公司，计划于2026年4月对长呼复线—大东管道联络线项目占地范围开展文物勘探工作。该项目位于内蒙古自治区鄂尔多斯市伊金霍洛旗苏布尔嘎镇，总用地面积为82339平方米。鉴于项目范围内部分区域存在道路及地下管道，尚不具备全面勘探条件，本次拟考古勘探面积为37835平方米。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "根据指导意见，现将长呼复线—大东管道联络线项目文物勘探计划随文呈报并请贵局予以审批备案。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "1.5",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman Regular"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "此请示，请复。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 24.0,
      "left_indent_pt": null,
      "right_indent_pt": null,
